.TH hsh 1 "June 2025" "0.1" "Simple Shell Manual"

.SH NAME
hsh \- simple shell, command line interpreter

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hsh
.RI [ command ]

.SH DESCRIPTION
hsh is a simple UNIX shell that can run commands and interpret input both interactively and non-interactively.

.SH OPTIONS
The hsh shell has no options.

.SH COMMANDS
The following built-in commands are supported:
.TP
.B exit
Exit the shell.

.SH EXAMPLES
.B ./hsh
Starts the shell.

.SH AUTHOR
Written by Kamogelo Modise.
